recipesJson.name: Venomous Kangaroos
recipesJson.author: SlashaLO
recipesJson.description: Congratulations Australia! When people come together they can get things done. This is a throw you you guys! A nice and simple vape based of a nice and simple snack. White bread with some butter and sugar sprinkles. Sweeten to taste. I will say I have not tried this, but I have Sprinkles on order right now so I will try it. This is more of a theorycraft mix.
